    <p>
      See the Field Notes chapter for more detailed summaries and discussions of individual sources.
    </p>

    <dl>
      <li>
        <title>Primary Research</title>
        <p>
          Peer-reviewed papers and foundational works.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
