  <subsection xml:id="subsec-how-to-access">
    <title>How to Access Sources</title>
    <p>
      Most sources listed are available through:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><p><url href="https://arxiv.org">arXiv</url> - preprints</p></li>
      <li><p><url href="https://scholar.google.com">Google Scholar</url> - search</p></li>
      <li><p><url href="https://libgen.rs">Library Genesis</url> - books (check copyright)</p></li>
      <li><p><url href="https://sci-hub.se">Sci-Hub</url> - papers (check copyright)</p></li>
      <li><p>University/institutional access if available</p></li>
    </ul>
  </subsection>

</section>
